    org.apache.hbase.thirdparty.com.google.protobuf.Service
    Deprecated. 
    Keep it here only for compatibility with RSGroupAdminClient, using MasterRpcServices instead.

    @Deprecated
class RSGroupAdminServiceImpl
extends org.apache.hadoop.hbase.shaded.protobuf.generated.RSGroupAdminProtos.RSGroupAdminService
    Implementation of RSGroupAdminService defined in RSGroupAdmin.proto. This class calls RSGroupInfoManagerImpl for actual work, converts result to protocol buffer response, handles exceptions if any occurred and then calls the RpcCallback with the response.
